    <updated>2018-12-18T03:42:35.958Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>一、<strong>本地部署</strong><br>git <a href="https://git-scm.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://git-scm.com</a><br>node.js <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/en/</a><br>官方下载并一路默认安装<br>打开CMD命令行</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo init d:\blog\hexo</span><br><span class="line">d:</span><br><span class="line">cd blog\hexo</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong># 命令详情参考官方文档：</strong><br><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands.html</a></p><p><strong>正常的话，此时已可以通过浏览器访问“localhost:4000”打开本地搭建的网页了<br>（hexo s 这个窗口不能关闭）</strong></p><p>小技巧：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g -w</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s -s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同时运行这2条命令，可实现本地网站内容更改后的实时更新。</p><p><strong>二、发布至Github</strong></p><p>1、注册Github</p><p>2、相关配置</p><ul><li>打开CMD命令行：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 git config --global user.name &quot;Github用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">2 git config --global user.email &quot;Github注册邮箱&quot;</span><br><span class="line">3 ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;Github注册邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>**打开”.ssh”目录下的“id_rsa.pub”,全选复制。</p><p>去Github网站添加密钥（粘贴刚才复制的内容）。**</p><p>更改网站配置文件的如下部分：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 deploy:</span><br><span class="line">2   type: git</span><br><span class="line">3   repo: 仓库地址.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><em>CMD命令行进入本地网站主目录：</em></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3、<strong>上传网站</strong></p><ul><li>CMD进入本地网站主目录：</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">2 hexo g</span><br><span class="line">3 hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>至此一切顺利的话，访问Github域名即可看到生成的网站了。备注：由于我的安装路径有问题，故必须用node   %appdata%\npm\node_modules\hexo-cli\bin\hexo 才能进行博客建立和部署。</em></p>]]></content>
    
